
// The code recursively lists all folders within a specified directory, including hidden and system folders. The [io.folder.list-recursively] slot is used to perform the recursive listing, with [display-hidden] set to true to include hidden folders, and [display-system] set to the value of a specified argument to determine if system folders should be displayed.
io.folder.list-recursively:x:@.arguments/*/folder
   display-hidden:bool:true
   display-system:x:@.arguments/*/sys
